home becomes your classroom.\n\nNext Expansion: \nSpace: Kitchen\nSpace: Bedroom\nMain Language: French\nLearning Language: Spanish / espa\u00f1ol \nLearning Language: English\nMini-Game: Sentence Scramble", "short_description": "Transform your language learning experience. \n\nUtilizing mixed-reality passthrough technology turn your home into a dynamic classroom. Tag real-world objects in your living room with 470+ customizable tags for learning French. Sharpen your skills through the Word Shuffle mini-game.\n\nFluentXR is an ever-evolving platform, updating with new languages, locations, and interactive mini-games. Dive into a context-rich home environment that's both captivating and practical."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Fluent XR Mobile Icon.png", "id": "2236631716529956", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974513_2236631719863289_7778467312643440417_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=0aIRNg5E5lEQ7kNvgEKmxj0&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AKlD3shROvt6h5BhcTxire-&oh=00_AYBr0njON5SdxLzlPz-R0MeSS0bKV9v3Rmw0SufZ3SZZRg&oe=66F13A95"}, {"file_name": "Fluent XR PDP Art.png", "id": "2055286771488876", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974466_2055286774822209_4338361723960595313_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=NWe_5RAQO-EQ7kNvgE2bdES&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AKlD3shROvt6h5BhcTxire-&oh=00_AYDY3uNckUDMAK9A1KA3rcacrDekt8xJgBxZ9eMrlJpolA&oe=66F157A7"}, {"file_name": "Fluent XR Cover Art.png", "id": "678364797690874", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974640_678364801024207_2897138990588590099_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=zBiyrA87z_YQ7kNvgHuzoxi&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AKlD3shROvt6h5BhcTxire-&oh=00_AYCDK-A7qNLuGzNAABlJ9IZRpvCD2PvTA1iXVxc9ICgvEg&oe=66F15DAB"}, {"file_name": "Fluent XR Logo transparent.png", "id": "21284538